casebody.data:
SINNOCK et al., Respondents, v. PRATT, Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. May 18, 1894.) Action by William P. Sinnock and others against Charles L. Pratt.

Argued before VAN BRUNT, P. J, and FOLLETT and PARKER, JJ.

A. Crook, for appellant. A. Blumenstiel, for respondents.

No opinion. Order affirmed, with $10 costs and disbursements.
